# 🧠 TaskFlow – Productivity & Task Management App

> 🚀 A solo full-stack project built for the Holberton School Web Stack Portfolio  
> 👤 Developed by Melek Maolla | 🗓️ 2024

---

## 📌 Overview

**TaskFlow** is a Trello-inspired task management web application designed to boost team productivity and collaboration. It allows users to create boards, organize tasks with drag-and-drop functionality, assign priorities, and manage workflows intuitively. Built using modern web technologies, it provides a smooth and responsive user experience across devices.

---

