---

## 🎯 Features

- ✅ Secure user authentication with Clerk
- ✅ Create and manage multiple boards
- ✅ Add, edit, and drag-and-drop tasks between columns
- ✅ Assign priorities and deadlines
- ✅ Real-time updates via webhooks
- ✅ Responsive and modern UI with Shadcn and Lucide
- ✅ Fetch API communication with backend (Django)

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Frontend                  | Backend             | Database     | Auth & API | UI/UX           |
|--------------------------|---------------------|--------------|------------|-----------------|
| React (with Hooks)       | Django REST Framework | PostgreSQL   | Clerk      | Shadcn UI, Lucide |
| Fetch API                | Django Webhooks     |              |            | CSS Modules     |

