## 📈 Project Highlights

### ✅ Successes
- Built a solo full-stack application from scratch
- Clean, responsive, and modern UI design
- Integrated secure Clerk authentication and session management
- Implemented task drag-and-drop and real-time updates using webhooks

### ❌ Challenges
- Integrating Clerk with Django’s backend logic
- Handling state management and performance on large task boards
- Managing asynchronous updates between client and server

### 📚 What I Learned
- Full-stack project architecture and integration
- Clerk authentication and secure front-end/back-end session flow
- Django REST API design and PostgreSQL ORM
- UI/UX optimization and modern frontend design with Shadcn

### 🧩 Improvements & Next Steps
- 🔄 Real-time collaboration using WebSockets
- 📲 Mobile app version (React Native)
- 🔔 In-app notifications and reminders
- 📊 Analytics dashboard for productivity tracking

